# Datapacks go here
# Datapacks are world-specific and will be copied to world/datapacks/ on first boot.
# Place your .zip datapack files here.
#
# Example structure:
#   datapacks/
#   ├── my-datapack-1.zip
#   ├── my-datapack-2.zip
#   └── another-pack/
#       └── data/
#           └── (datapack contents)
#
# Each datapack must be:
# - A valid Minecraft datapack ZIP or directory
# - Compatible with Minecraft 1.21.4 (configured in mods/manifest.yaml)
#
# Datapacks are loaded by the server at startup from world/datapacks/
